♪Make a wish,
like it's going to come true♪

00:34:38.900 --> 00:34:46.700
♪Time will convey your answer♪

00:34:46.700 --> 00:34:53.820
♪You say you want
to search the distance♪

00:34:53.820 --> 00:35:00.420
♪Smiling, I hope everything
will remain as it is♪

00:35:01.620 --> 00:35:08.420
♪The night wind blows, my eyes reddened♪

00:35:08.860 --> 00:35:15.460
♪Thoughts sink below the vast ocean♪

00:35:16.260 --> 00:35:23.460
♪The night wind blows, disorienting me♪

00:35:23.460 --> 00:35:29.380
♪Those who go and never return,
they sadden me♪

00:35:29.380 --> 00:35:33.420
♪I'm lost♪

