keeps memories of the past♪

00:36:22.020 --> 00:36:29.620
♪Every wish is a star that still shines♪

00:36:30.020 --> 00:36:37.180
♪Whenever I feel down and helpless♪

00:36:37.180 --> 00:36:43.620
♪I look at it, and everything
